# Optional Proxy Configuration
# Use an HTTPS/SOCKS5 proxy to bypass xHamster's IP detection
# Example:
# HTTP_PROXY=http://your-proxy-ip:port
# HTTPS_PROXY=http://your-proxy-ip:port
# Or SOCKS5:
# HTTP_PROXY=socks5://your-proxy-ip:port
# HTTPS_PROXY=socks5://your-proxy-ip:port

# Uncomment and set your proxy here:
# HTTP_PROXY=
# HTTPS_PROXY=
